## Dashboard 1: Databricks Platform Overview

• Overall cost tracking and trends
• Monthly workspace usage metrics
• Product usage breakdown by service
• SKU consumption analysis

## Dashboard 2: Granular Cost Analysis

• Time-based cost views (daily/weekly/monthly/yearly)
• Cost drivers by product, SKU, and project
• High-cost jobs and cluster analysis
• Top spending by node type and users

## Dashboard 3: Azure Cost Integration

• Total current month costs
• Billing period comparisons
• Cost breakdown by Azure service
• Top 10 highest-cost resources​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​